{"tid":166093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（Design)支那鐵路穿民宅而過勁慳位！","createTime":"2017-03-22T00:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T04:06:46.000Z","uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e8fb689e4fe5451e9bdd234f85763cc3ca89911","tid":166093,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:14:38.000Z","msg":"綜合外媒報導，中國重慶輕軌的2號線在經過李子壩段落時，會開進一棟19層高的大樓，然後從大樓的另一側穿出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這棟被輕軌穿越大樓的1樓到5樓是商舖，9樓到19樓則是住宅，而大樓中間的6樓到8樓則被規劃為軌道交通區域。6樓是站廳，7樓是設備層，8樓則是站台層，大樓中被輕軌所穿越的地方長達132公尺。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n這樣奇特的輕軌設計吸引《每日郵報》、《鏡報》、《每日電訊報》等外媒進行報導，外國網友也對此議論紛紛。有網友直言，「真為住這棟大樓的住戶感到可憐。」、「輕軌造成的噪音一定吵死人了...」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php81nrBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php81nrBj.jpg&h=2cb3b10d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"805a7c0f9f8bb650de91ade6a0b66e11aa60be01","tid":166093,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:17:30.000Z","msg":"超為單軌鐵路上蓋物業一種形式"},{"pid":"a18c82f66eb20cc41983c9eed0c54e1705881150","tid":166093,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"唔嘈架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e6be7e859ab5b539f4b752eb4bdd7819aa5dbb","tid":166093,"uid":1494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:22:32.000Z","msg":"青衣城唔係都係咁款咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e439fb9a6c8e6971e19c9cdb6c713e7b9ceab6","tid":166093,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔嘈架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n單軌列車用橡膠輪胎，較鐵輪式列車寧靜；<br />\n噪音只係冷氣機及牽引系統，不過細聲得多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9e2cdc1bfa7e9c7814ea63b1b82240d11cab3d","tid":166093,"ui